{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9a8aeb2dd","title":"在中央常委扩大会上的四点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"706b1dc31f","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bbd3a2a41a","type":"title","text":"在中央常委扩大会上的四点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5a5fb0267","type":"paragraph","text":"一、大家要挺身而出，同群众见面，接受群众的批评，并进行自我批评，引火烧身","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98090ebd87","type":"paragraph","text":"二、大家要挺身而出，向群众解释政策。戴高帽子、抹黑脸的，脱帽洗脸，立即上班工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f88d2af7b5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、从长远利益出发，团结多数。牛鬼蛇神就是地、富、反、坏、右少数。有些人就是犯了严重错误，还得换救他，使之改过自新。不然，怎么能团结百分之九十五以上呢","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f364ec59a","type":"paragraph","text":"四、说服干部，使他们懂得，不要人人过关，都搞得灰溜溜的，两个挺身而出，不要怕字当头。敢字当头，最大的问题也能解决。怕字当头，价钱越来越高","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e9a8aeb2dd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":249,"end":249}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"11fc3ceb75","type":"paragraph","text":"